>\n巴打 你睇黎有d歷練 wor</blockquote><br />\n笑撚死人</blockquote><br />\n自欺欺人咪會咁講<br />\n有時安慰人都會咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇咁大個頭就唔好學人戴咁大頂帽"},{"pid":"7aa33b30293f4e0fcdc9185995a7319da0f7ee00","tid":336902,"uid":44504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成班on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為長處 = 一樣可以贏到全世界既技能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你要蠃既只有你自己<br />\n每日都同自己講要超越自己<br />\n你先會有希望</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打 你睇黎有d歷練 wor</blockquote><br />\n笑撚死人</blockquote><br />\n on9 仔"},{"pid":"a044dd0667a88d72a0b19a23657427d1f568a08b","tid":336902,"uid":11973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:05:59.000Z","msg":"唔緊要<br />\n呢個只係成長經歷嘅過程<br />\n好快過多十年八年<br />\n你人生嘅座佑銘就會變成「是鳩但啦」㗎喇<br />\n當你去到呢一步嘅時候就證明你真係成熟喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599e4f1f8e6e3ad5c021b05897190796e5ed9197","tid":336902,"uid":111256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:22:29.000Z","msg":"大家都明要贏自己既道理<br />\n<br />\n但 競技活動 贏自己係無用的"},{"pid":"8b510d40be5ca875fbd9aa90b7ed705e279846da","tid":336902,"uid":39921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:26:37.000Z","msg":"做人無愧於心就夠<br />\n要用比較黎獲得快樂，最後只會獲得痛苦"},{"pid":"52ce329f9feb8b73b6d4ce8305f1f15ed01eb748","tid":336902,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:39:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9fb6c06f6c723b434a1330971e643fbe039a519","tid":336902,"uid":121546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:57:52.000Z","msg":"不過以大部份人既努力程度黎講跟本去唔到要講天份既階段"},{"pid":"f3fb308490a59a6acef80b6b59552e963e0ce15f","tid":336902,"uid":111256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:01:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你返緊咩工？</blockquote><br />\n辦公室文職"},{"pid":"45a986501ad05b80be2242a11c42c8ef668d4b78","tid":336902,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家都明要贏自己既道理<br />\n<br />\n但 競技活動 贏自己係無用的</blockquote><br />\n運動，玩得緊係想嬴<br />\n但嬴家既位置永遠得一個<br />\n你諗返一開始點解會選擇打波，點解會花咁多時間去訓練<br />\n熱門既，一年有幾次公開賽可以打下<br />\n冷門既，我試過一年得一季賽期，打完個幾場就無，然後又要再花一年時間練波。<br />\n諗下平時係乜野支撐你做落去仲好啦。<br />\n打比賽就話嬴係最大目標<br />\n平日訓練每一日都係超越自我既訓練"},{"pid":"190381e6f9020f857010f24f7ad7b7bdaed4ffac","tid":336902,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T10:10:15.000Z","msg":"巴打 你已經好努力了 做人盡咗力就得㗎喇 <br />\n生活從來都不易 唔係所有事都係如自己所料"},{"pid":"1a04c53651343509e7fbd6da1c48eec6497ebd38","tid":336902,"uid":92951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T10:40:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔緊要<br />\n呢個只係成長經歷嘅過程<br />\n好快過多十年八年<br />\n你人生嘅座佑銘就會變成「是鳩但啦」㗎喇<br />\n當你去到呢一步嘅時候就證明你真係成熟喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我由中學個時已經係咁<br />\n而家做野都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ece743019c4c13fad8fade9beeb767f361638dd","tid":336902,"uid":35857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"屌 我都係踢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇天份真係輸九成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a00b3335210f7ba77cd654b5b0ee2785fef187","tid":336902,"uid":57232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T10:45:15.000Z","msg":"點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4679122f089b9156c2dba655e71e930fe59d65b1","tid":336902,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T10:51:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"022e2bfc63152c76c13c8111eb44ba7bd9a860ea","tid":336902,"uid":125590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T16:06:50.000Z","msg":"唔好放棄呀，唔好拎呢一刻去同人比，依家做唔到，將來可以做得到，你做唔到你既下一代都可以做得到，世界上有人需要你，人係可以一dd咁去改變世界，我等緊樓主番英文post 繼續教英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1692ed111eb5781af3769ab8417c9b3c8125111","tid":336902,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T03:28:35.000Z","msg":"猿生究竟幾時先可以醒覺<br />\n<br />\n利申: 只有小聰明,無長處<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072dc680bcdddf69a468621038b79f06a9564de5","tid":336902,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T03:33:35.000Z","msg":"係咁啦<br />\n世界咁大你想贏晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定有勁過你既人"},{"pid":"b690d31a2498f2bccab6fd2738f47db5f935541c","tid":336902,"uid":82006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:31:03.000Z","msg":"係你以為自己好努力姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68941cc247be03dd5fb8ae03dea9cdbf3ef20cd","tid":336902,"uid":111256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T13:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好放棄呀，唔好拎呢一刻去同人比，依家做唔到，將來可以做得到，你做唔到你既下一代都可以做得到，世界上有人需要你，人係可以一dd咁去改變世界，我等緊樓主番英文post 繼續教英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔講唔記得原來有讀書"},{"pid":"b0891ef9713d01fe618aaeb0e71241bd2bec0eda","tid":336902,"uid":111256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T13:12:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好放棄呀，唔好拎呢一刻去同人比，依家做唔到，將來可以做得到，你做唔到你既下一代都可以做得到，世界上有人需要你，人係可以一dd咁去改變世界，我等緊樓主番英文post 繼續教英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔講唔記得原來有讀者</blockquote>"},{"pid":"586bba7a1d9e91322f51a30c6d2d2723878a459d","tid":336902,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T13:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0782d0f933ac7ddd876d237e1fd2190224d334","tid":336902,"uid":28002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T03:45:33.000Z","msg":"又係自怨自艾叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你做乜呢個世界都大把人叻過你架啦<br />\n如果下下都咁樣諗你應該乜都唔洗做<br />\n<br />\n一唔夠人黎就賴天份<br />\n不如問返自己有幾努力先？"},{"pid":"ec442cd41b6b4d70e48cf1ae7e0d5d3860da564a","tid":336902,"uid":65774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T04:24:49.000Z","msg":"有d野天份係佔9成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我細個以為自己畫畫好叻，<br />\n其實我只係識素描<br />\n由細開始都堅信自己有畫畫天份，<br />\nkeep住學畫畫<br />\n果陣以自己小學已經畫到人像素描為榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但當我上左中學，發現原來art唔係得素描<br />\n我初中Art仲試過唔合格，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為除左素描既作品外，我全部都好差<br />\n唔識手工唔識用廣告彩唔識用粉彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果時既我仲安慰自己：<br />\n我係畫畫好叻既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過由中四揀左Va開始就仆街，<br />\n學校規定大家要做設計，<br />\n我開始發現其實素描完全係無撚用<br />\n同埋我係無art天份，<br />\n因為重點係我其實係一個完全無創意既人<br />\n果陣做一份作品我都想死咁制，<br />\n做完就係合格與唔合格邊緣<br />\n每日番學都好憎上Va堂<br />\n反觀其他同學，雖然畫野唔岩比例但好撚有創意<br />\n同埋又識用其他媒介畫野，符合哂老師要求<br />\n而我淨係識揸筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是我開始回頭發現其實我一d長處都無，<br />\n我信左10幾年既所謂畫畫叻其實係假<br />\n真係好撚唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到之後接近10年我已經無左揸過筆畫野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能驚一揸筆就諗起自己係一無是處既廢物"},{"pid":"88f2493c60203dc8e1e38488a3a0a652c448fc99","tid":336902,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T04:25:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家都明要贏自己既道理<br />\n<br />\n但 競技活動 贏自己係無用的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb3109a5abfd3e8583e51de4454976a383ba262","tid":336902,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T04:26:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做人無愧於心就夠<br />\n要用比較黎獲得快樂，最後只會獲得痛苦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1264920b5604256c5dd0d433aa2ef07e9cf67a2d","tid":336902,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T04:26:57.000Z","msg":"我跳到盡只可以蚊框 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850f5fe293338294031769763614cd61a0c3f46e","tid":336902,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T04:28:52.000Z","msg":"或者你太安穩 先咁樣都唔滿足"},{"pid":"ded5352e9e2e3f18d69fb3b49aad50002b014ccd","tid":336902,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T04:29:04.000Z","msg":"玩開運動一到感受到呢句 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}